":"HA嘅護士課程唔係講笑<br />\n佢嘅教學方式同其他差好遠<br />\n而且其他有得用 大學嘅設施但係佢咩都無<br />\n佢教完就考，教完就考<br />\n聽人講係<br />\n兩個星期一小測，一個月一大測<br />\nFail一定次數就直接踢你走<br />\n因為學費由醫管局成數資助<br />\n所以嚴撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">感覺上行內人普遍對醫管局嘅護士學生有更高要求，做錯少少就俾人屌到仆街</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ff5f6773c2a0104fab49e28d882187233351b01","tid":670772,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"醫管局都有個高級文憑<br />\n有咩分別？"},{"pid":"0a43132e445c621064dbd4f654d7d60e112e4e25","tid":670772,"uid":56567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ff5f6773c2a0104fab49e28d882187233351b01","tid":670772,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"醫管局都有個高級文憑<br />\n有咩分別？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"rn"},{"pid":"417d5435ba63f780ea104b1b43e918dc685a33e5","tid":670772,"uid":5336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"前世做錯事"},{"pid":"78e80c60f9a52f20cef609a36936dc22fa26d73d","tid":670772,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417d5435ba63f780ea104b1b43e918dc685a33e5","tid":670772,"uid":5336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"前世做錯事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"今世做護士"},{"pid":"906daa31d251929a209e5dfae32a63a3d2eb1c0b","tid":670772,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78e80c60f9a52f20cef609a36936dc22fa26d73d","tid":670772,"uid":15503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417d5435ba63f780ea104b1b43e918dc685a33e5","tid":670772,"uid":5336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"前世做錯事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"今世做護士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"冇得簡先會做護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa452b9a514e